Description: h2. Feature: Contract Notice Search and Results

URL: [https://www.tenders.gov.au/cn/search|https://www.tenders.gov.au/cn/search]

·         Given I navigate to [https://www.tenders.gov.au/cn/search|https://www.tenders.gov.au/cn/search]

·         When I select 'Publish Date' and input date range '01/01/2024 to 31/03/2025'

·         And I click on the button View

·         Then I should see a list of contract notices with publish date, agency, and value
